---
import Base from '../layouts/base.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Base title="Privacy Policy — Beebeeb" description="How Beebeeb handles your data. GDPR-compliant, zero-knowledge by design, EU-only infrastructure.">
  <Nav />

  <section class="px-8 pt-14 pb-20 bg-paper">
    <div class="max-w-[760px] mx-auto">
      <div class="text-[10.5px] font-semibold tracking-[0.04em] uppercase text-ink-3 mb-2">Legal</div>
      <h1 class="text-[32px] font-semibold tracking-[-0.03em]">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-ink-2 mt-2 leading-relaxed">
        Effective 1 January 2026 &middot; Initlabs B.V. &middot; KvK 95157565
      </p>

      <div class="mt-10 space-y-10 text-[14px] text-ink-2 leading-[1.75]">

        <!-- 1 -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-2">1. Who we are</h2>
          <p>Beebeeb is operated by Initlabs B.V., registered at Kelvinstraat 34A, 6601 HE Wijchen, Netherlands (KvK 95157565). We are the data controller for the personal data described in this policy.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- 2 -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-2">2. What we collect</h2>
          <div class="mt-3 border border-line rounded-[10px] overflow-hidden">
            {[
              ['Email address', 'Account registration, communication', 'Contract performance'],
              ['Password hash', 'Authentication (we never store your password in plain text)', 'Contract performance'],
              ['Payment information', 'Processed by Stripe; we store a reference, not card details', 'Contract performance'],
              ['Encrypted file blobs', 'Storing your files (we cannot read their contents)', 'Contract performance'],
              ['Access logs', 'IP address, user agent, timestamps for security and abuse prevention', 'Legitimate interest'],
            ].map(([data, purpose, basis], i, arr) => (
              <div class:list={['grid grid-cols-[1fr_1.4fr_auto] gap-4 px-4 py-3 text-[12.5px]', i < arr.length - 1 ? 'border-b border-line' : '']}>
                <span class="font-semibold text-ink">{data}</span>
                <span>{purpose}</span>
                <span class="font-mono text-[11px] text-ink-3">{basis}</span>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 3 -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-2">3. What we do not collect</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-1.5 list-disc list-inside">
            <li><strong>File contents</strong> — encrypted on your device; we cannot read them</li>
            <li><strong>Filenames</strong> — encrypted alongside your files</li>
            <li><strong>Analytics or tracking</strong> — no analytics SDKs in the app</li>
            <li><strong>Cookies beyond session authentication</strong> — no third-party cookies, no tracking pixels</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- 4 -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-2">4. Sub-processors</h2>
          <p>We use the following sub-processors, all located in the EU:</p>
          <div class="mt-3 border border-line rounded-[10px] overflow-hidden">
            {[
              ['Hetzner', 'File storage, compute', 'Germany (DE)'],
              ['Leaseweb', 'File storage', 'Netherlands (NL)'],
              ['Stripe', 'Payment processing', 'Ireland (IE)'],
              ['Postmark', 'Transactional email', 'Germany (DE)'],
            ].map(([name, purpose, location], i, arr) => (
              <div class:list={['grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 px-4 py-3 text-[12.5px]', i < arr.length - 1 ? 'border-b border-line' : '']}>
                <span class="font-semibold text-ink">{name}</span>
                <span>{purpose}</span>
                <span class="font-mono text-[11px] text-ink-3">{location}</span>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
          <p class="mt-3">No data leaves the EU. When you create an account, you choose your storage region.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- 5 -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-2">5. Data residency</h2>
          <p>All data is stored in the European Union. You choose your storage region at account creation (Germany or Netherlands). We do not transfer data outside the EU and have no US-based sub-processors.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- 6 -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-2">6. Your rights</h2>
          <p>Under the GDPR, you have the following rights:</p>
          <div class="mt-3 border border-line rounded-[10px] overflow-hidden">
            {[
              ['Access (Art. 15)', 'Request a copy of the personal data we hold about you'],
              ['Rectification (Art. 16)', 'Correct inaccurate personal data'],
              ['Erasure (Art. 17)', 'Request deletion of your personal data'],
              ['Portability (Art. 20)', 'Receive your data in a structured, machine-readable format'],
              ['Object (Art. 21)', 'Object to processing based on legitimate interest'],
            ].map(([right, desc], i, arr) => (
              <div class:list={['grid grid-cols-[auto_1fr] gap-4 px-4 py-3 text-[12.5px]', i < arr.length - 1 ? 'border-b border-line' : '']}>
                <span class="font-semibold text-ink">{right}</span>
                <span>{desc}</span>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
          <p class="mt-3">To exercise any of these rights, email <span class="font-mono text-xs">privacy@beebeeb.io</span>. We respond within 30 days.</p>
          <p class="mt-2">Note: because your files are encrypted with keys we do not hold, we cannot provide decrypted copies of your file data. We can provide all personal data we do hold (email, logs, metadata).</p>
        </div>

        <!-- 7 -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-2">7. Retention</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-1.5 list-disc list-inside">
            <li><strong>Active account data</strong> — kept for as long as your account exists</li>
            <li><strong>Deleted data</strong> — encrypted blobs are shredded within 30 days of account deletion</li>
            <li><strong>Audit logs</strong> — retained for 13 months, then deleted</li>
            <li><strong>Invoices and billing records</strong> — retained for 7 years as required by Dutch tax law</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- 8 -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-2">8. Security</h2>
          <p>We protect your data with:</p>
          <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1.5 list-disc list-inside">
            <li>Zero-knowledge, end-to-end encryption (AES-256-GCM, Argon2id, X25519)</li>
            <li>TLS 1.3 with HSTS preload for all connections</li>
            <li>Regular third-party security audits (published on our <a class="text-amber-deep" href="/security">security page</a>)</li>
            <li>An active <a class="text-amber-deep" href="/bug-bounty">bug bounty program</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- 9 -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-2">9. Changes to this policy</h2>
          <p>We may update this privacy policy. When we make material changes, we will email you at least 30 days before they take effect. The current version is always available at this URL.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- 10 -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-2">10. Contact and complaints</h2>
          <div class="mt-3 bg-paper-2 border border-line rounded-[10px] p-5">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-[auto_1fr] gap-x-6 gap-y-2 text-[12.5px]">
              <span class="font-semibold text-ink">Data Protection Officer</span>
              <span class="font-mono text-[12px]">privacy@beebeeb.io</span>
              <span class="font-semibold text-ink">Postal address</span>
              <span>Initlabs B.V., Kelvinstraat 34A, 6601 HE Wijchen, Netherlands</span>
              <span class="font-semibold text-ink">Supervisory authority</span>
              <span>Autoriteit Persoonsgegevens (Dutch Data Protection Authority) &middot; <a class="text-amber-deep" href="https://autoriteitpersoonsgegevens.nl" target="_blank" rel="noopener">autoriteitpersoonsgegevens.nl</a></span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-3">If you are not satisfied with our response, you have the right to lodge a complaint with the Autoriteit Persoonsgegevens.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Base>
